                <head>No. 116.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hoffman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-04-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 27, 1876</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Fish</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary, Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>If Winslow gets before Queen’s Bench on <hi rend="italic">habeas corpus</hi>, am
                    I to employ counsel? Shall not intervene unless instructed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HOFFMAN,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Chargé</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
